@host = https://localhost:7443
@tenant = 11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111
@user = 22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222

### Health
GET {{host}}/health

### List categories (system defaults) — dev auth
GET {{host}}/api/v1/categories
X-Dev-Tenant: {{tenant}}
X-Dev-User: {{user}}
X-Dev-Role: Owner

### Provision a household (anonymous, signup)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/households
Content-Type: application/json

{ "householdName": "Fernandez", "ownerEmail": "me@example.com", "ownerExternalAuthId": "ext-1", "ownerDisplayName": "Me" }

### Create an account
POST {{host}}/api/v1/accounts
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
X-Dev-Tenant: {{tenant}}
X-Dev-User: {{user}}
X-Dev-Role: Owner

{ "name": "BBVA Debito", "type": "Checking", "institution": "BBVA", "currency": "MXN", "number": "1234567812345678" }

### Import a CSV statement (replace accountId)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/statements/csv
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
X-Dev-Tenant: {{tenant}}
X-Dev-User: {{user}}
X-Dev-Role: Owner

{ "accountId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000", "fileName": "enero.csv", "content": "Fecha,Concepto,Cargo,Abono\n2026-01-05,OXXO,150.00,\n2026-01-06,NOMINA,,12000.00\n" }

### Scan a receipt/ticket (multipart image → staged transaction via OCR; feature #49, replace accountId)
# The fake extractor reads a UTF-8 "receipt text" body in dev/CI, so this image content is a readable
# receipt; in prod the bytes are a real photo handled by Azure Document Intelligence (prebuilt-receipt).
POST {{host}}/api/v1/receipts
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
X-Dev-Tenant: {{tenant}}
X-Dev-User: {{user}}
X-Dev-Role: Owner
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=ReceiptBoundary

--ReceiptBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="accountId"

00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
--ReceiptBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="ticket.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

merchant: OXXO TIENDA 1234
date: 2026-01-15
total: 152.50
currency: MXN
confidence: 0.94
--ReceiptBoundary--

### List scanned receipts (OCR status + staged-transaction link)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/receipts
X-Dev-Tenant: {{tenant}}
X-Dev-User: {{user}}
X-Dev-Role: Owner

### Review queue — staged transactions from receipts/statements await confirm
GET {{host}}/api/v1/transactions/review
X-Dev-Tenant: {{tenant}}
X-Dev-User: {{user}}
X-Dev-Role: Owner

### Unified ledger feed
GET {{host}}/api/v1/ledger?confirmedOnly=false
X-Dev-Tenant: {{tenant}}
X-Dev-User: {{user}}
X-Dev-Role: Owner

### Net worth
GET {{host}}/api/v1/insights/net-worth
X-Dev-Tenant: {{tenant}}
X-Dev-User: {{user}}
X-Dev-Role: Owner

### Scan for alerts
POST {{host}}/api/v1/alerts/scan
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
X-Dev-Tenant: {{tenant}}
X-Dev-User: {{user}}
X-Dev-Role: Owner
